data.description: An entertainers dream!! This home has a marvelous floor-plan perfect for your family gatherings or entertaining. Utilize the large living area which is open to both the formal and casual dining spaces and easily overflows onto the large, partially covered patio. The master suite is of ample size and boasts a spa like bath with soaker tub and separate tile shower- close the door and forget about your day! Two additional downstairs bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bath. Upstairs you are treated to two additional very large bedrooms and a full bath. This home looks appealing from every angle and has great views of the lake as well. Wonderfully maintained and well cared for. *Hardwood floors  *Tile back splash *Granite counter tops *Roof *Siding *Garage door *Front entry door all recently updated  ***Stay comfortable with a Generac whole house generator!!*** Take the time to tour this one. Call today!
